                   <td class="statText" colspan="2">
                    We have the following weight relations:
                    <pre>
w0 &gt; w1 &gt; w2
w3 &gt; w4 &gt; w5</pre>
                    It can only be true if the values are (30,20,10,30,20,10). The left pan contains weights 1 and 4 with total weight
 20+20=40.
There is one pair (0,3) heavier than that, one pair (2,5) lighter than that and the remaining four pairs have the same weight.
                   </td>
